Headlines.Headline: Scripps Shares Drop Following Breakup Of Media Company

PARAGRAPH.#text: Shares of E.W. Scripps Co. (SSP) slumped Tuesday as its former cable television and Website assets began trading as a separate company following the long-awaited breakup of the media conglomerate.
